{{doc/start}}
Renders a sortable wikitable of all recipes craftable in a specific building, with columns for recipe name, inputs, outputs, and craft time. The building column is omitted since it is implicit. Backed by [[Module:RecipeTable]]'s <code>building</code> function.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{RecipeTable Building|_base_assembler_i}}
{{RecipeTable Building|id=_base_assembler_i}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Parameter !! Description !! Type !! Status
|-
| <code>1</code> / <code>id</code> || Building template identifier (e.g. <code>_base_assembler_i</code> for Assembler I, <code>_base_smelter_i</code> for Smelter I). || String || Required
|}

== Notes ==
* Recipes are looked up via [[Module:Data/BuildingRecipeIndex]], keyed by building template identifier.
* The Building column is suppressed in this view (it would always be the same building).
* For displaying recipes by item, use [[Template:RecipeTable]].
* If the building has no associated recipes, the template outputs nothing.
{{doc/end}}
